Description: Digital photograph (colour); view of engraved rock art showing two human figures and figures of three dogs, all upright, pecked in outline. At left is human figure infilled with pecking and face on, with outstretched arms, left hand holding straight object, right hand holding curved object. Dog is to right facing right. To right of this is pair of dogs facing left, human figure between them, facing right and holding staff. Aswan, Egypt. Scanned
Acquisition name: Donated by: Trust for African Rock Art
